31
00:03:12,759 --> 00:03:16,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pertama kali datang ke Goryeo
saat berusia 16 tahun.</font>

32
00:03:18,359 --> 00:03:21,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa berbicara menggunakan bahasa mereka,
dan orang-orang di sini membuatku takut.</font>

33
00:03:22,630 --> 00:03:25,299
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi dialah yang paling aneh
dan menakutkan.</font>

34
00:03:26,539 --> 00:03:28,169
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah aku menikah,</font>

35
00:03:29,009 --> 00:03:31,569
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia menjadi Raja.</font>

36
00:03:58,169 --> 00:04:00,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu mengapa
aku menceritakan...</font>

37
00:04:02,410 --> 00:04:04,069
<font color=#FFFF00>...cerita panjang seperti itu?</font>

38
00:04:04,069 --> 00:04:05,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

39
00:04:05,979 --> 00:04:09,509
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah menikah, hanya
ada satu tempat untukku bersandar.</font>

40
00:04:10,549 --> 00:04:12,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Anakku, Seja.</font>

41
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:18,419
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hidup untuk memberi
apa yang dia butuhkan, inginkan,</font>

42
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:21,289
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan untuk menyelamatkannya.</font>

43
00:04:23,289 --> 00:04:26,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahku juga mengatakan hal yang sama.</font>

44
00:04:26,859 --> 00:04:29,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Bahkan sekarang, orang-orang yang berada
di pihak Raja,</font>

45
00:04:29,129 --> 00:04:31,129
<font color=#FFFF00>...menghina Seja.</font>

46
00:04:31,770 --> 00:04:33,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka mencoba menggulingkannya...</font>

47
00:04:34,970 --> 00:04:37,640
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan bahkan membunuhnya.</font>

48
00:04:38,410 --> 00:04:39,939
<font color=#FFFF00>Membunuhnya?</font>

49
00:04:39,939 --> 00:04:41,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja butuh kekuasaan.</font>

50
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:46,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan untuk mendapatkan kekuasaan,
dia membutuhkan harta Ayahmu.</font>

51
00:04:49,419 --> 00:04:50,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan memberinya?</font>

52
00:05:01,499 --> 00:05:02,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada berita buruk.</font>

53
00:05:10,410 --> 00:05:11,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.</font>

54
00:05:12,239 --> 00:05:14,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah. Ayah.</font>

55
00:05:14,780 --> 00:05:17,379
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, kenapa Ayah
berbaring seperti ini?</font>

56
00:05:18,510 --> 00:05:22,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, buka matamu. Ayah!</font>

57
00:05:23,789 --> 00:05:26,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah. Ayah.</font>

58
00:05:28,119 --> 00:05:32,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Obat.
Ayah sudah minum obatnya?</font>

59
00:05:33,260 --> 00:05:34,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasti ada di suatu tempat.</font>

60
00:05:37,229 --> 00:05:38,939
<font color=#FFFF00>Dimana dia?/
San.</font>

61
00:05:38,939 --> 00:05:41,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia selalu membawa obatnya.
Kau tidak lihat?</font>

62
00:05:42,070 --> 00:05:43,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Dimana dia?</font>

63
00:05:45,879 --> 00:05:47,179
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa tidak ada disini?</font>

64
00:05:50,249 --> 00:05:51,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.</font>

65
00:05:52,150 --> 00:05:53,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa tanganmu sangat dingin?</font>

66
00:05:56,419 --> 00:05:59,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, tolong jawab.</font>

67
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:02,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika Ayah minum obatnya,
Ayah akan segera bangun.</font>

68
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:05,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.</font>

69
00:06:06,629 --> 00:06:08,499
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kenapa wajahnya sangat dingin?</font>

70
00:06:08,499 --> 00:06:11,299
<font color=#FFFF00>Jantungnya tiba-tiba berhenti.</font>

71
00:06:11,799 --> 00:06:14,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pasti menderita penyakit kronis.</font>

72
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:16,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pasti sangat kesakitan.</font>

73
00:06:16,770 --> 00:06:20,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak lihat obat di
kertas putihnya?</font>

74
00:06:20,140 --> 00:06:22,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika dia minum obat itu...
kertasnya pasti ada di suatu tempat.</font>

75
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:24,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan tahu jika sudah ketemu itu.</font>

76
00:06:25,150 --> 00:06:27,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada tulisan "Cheon Yeol"
di atas kertasnya.</font>

77
00:06:36,090 --> 00:06:37,189
<font color=#FFFF00>San.</font>

78
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:41,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Obat.</font>

79
00:06:43,900 --> 00:06:45,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Obatnya ada di sana.</font>

80
00:06:47,239 --> 00:06:50,669
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, tunggu sebentar.
Aku akan mengambil obatmu.</font>

81
00:07:08,390 --> 00:07:10,330
<font color=#FFFF00>San. San.</font>

82
00:07:10,330 --> 00:07:12,830
<font color=#FFFF00>San, tenanglah. San!</font>

83
00:07:21,140 --> 00:07:22,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Ketemu.</font>

84
00:07:24,770 --> 00:07:26,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan./
Aku sudah menemukan obatnya.</font>

85
00:07:27,010 --> 00:07:29,609
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bilang hentikan./
Dia harus minum obat ini.</font>

86
00:07:29,710 --> 00:07:31,179
<font color=#FFFF00>San, sadarlah.</font>

87
00:07:34,749 --> 00:07:35,749
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi...</font>

88
00:07:46,700 --> 00:07:48,669
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa obatnya ada disini?</font>

89
00:07:56,210 --> 00:07:57,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksud dia?</font>

90
00:08:43,920 --> 00:08:45,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah menunggumu.</font>

91
00:08:52,259 --> 00:08:53,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Tuan Lin.</font>

92
00:08:54,259 --> 00:08:57,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harusnya pergi
berburu dengan Raja.</font>

93
00:08:58,170 --> 00:09:00,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau memanggilku?</font>

94
00:09:00,970 --> 00:09:04,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan memberitahumu lagi.
Aku bukan musuhmu.</font>

95
00:09:04,269 --> 00:09:06,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku diberitahu kalau
Tuan Eun dalam bahaya.</font>

96
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu umpan palsu?</font>

97
00:09:09,180 --> 00:09:12,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Seberapa banyak kau mengenal
Putri Won Sung?</font>

98
00:09:14,580 --> 00:09:17,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa menebak
betapa bahaya nya dia.</font>

99
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:21,259
<font color=#FFFF00>Pangeran Gang Yang ada di sini.</font>

100
00:09:28,430 --> 00:09:30,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Anak sulung Raja.</font>

101
00:09:30,170 --> 00:09:32,639
<font color=#FFFF00>Anak bibimu, Putri Jeong Hwa.</font>

102
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:33,869
<font color=#FFFF00>Pria yang...</font>

103
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:36,540
<font color=#FFFF00>...seharusnya menjadi Seja.</font>

104
00:09:37,739 --> 00:09:39,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang dia lakukan di sini?</font>

105
00:09:40,940 --> 00:09:42,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kau rencanakan?</font>

106
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia berumur 16 tahun...</font>

107
00:09:43,850 --> 00:09:46,450
<font color=#FFFF00>...ketika Putri Won Sung
datang ke Goryeo...</font>

108
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,379
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk menikah dengan Raja kita.</font>

109
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:05,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Di sinilah kamarku.</font>

110
00:10:05,470 --> 00:10:08,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa datang kapanpun.</font>

111
00:10:13,340 --> 00:10:15,979
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Hal pertama yang dilakukan
Putri Won Sung...</i></font>

112
00:10:15,979 --> 00:10:18,580
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...adalah membuat
Putri Jeong Hwa menjadi selir.</i></font>

113
00:10:22,290 --> 00:10:23,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Pangeran kecilku.</font>

114
00:10:24,519 --> 00:10:25,619
<font color=#FFFF00>Cilukba.</font>

115
00:10:27,359 --> 00:10:30,489
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tahun berikutnya, setelah dia
memiliki putra,</i></font>

116
00:10:30,859 --> 00:10:33,999
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dia menjadi lebih kejam lagi.</i></font>

117
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:39,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia membuat cucu
Kubilai Khan menangis.</font>

118
00:10:40,970 --> 00:10:44,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Beraninya kau membuat
keturunan Kaisar menangis?</font>

119
00:10:48,580 --> 00:10:51,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan marah, Ratu.</font>

120
00:10:51,279 --> 00:10:53,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau membuat anakku menangis!</font>

121
00:11:02,830 --> 00:11:05,899
<font color=#FFFF00>Pangeran Gang Yang ada di sini.</font>

122
00:11:07,259 --> 00:11:09,999
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tinggal bersamaku secara rahasia.</font>

123
00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:19,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Kudengar dia tinggal di kuil.</font>

124
00:11:19,279 --> 00:11:21,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Kuil mungkin bisa berbahaya.</font>

125
00:11:22,550 --> 00:11:24,109
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu?</font>

126
00:11:24,109 --> 00:11:26,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Entah di sini atau di
sana, dia masih hidup.</font>

127
00:11:26,820 --> 00:11:29,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami khawatir akan keselamatannya.</font>

128
00:11:30,519 --> 00:11:34,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Dialah yang seharusnya menjadi
Pangeran Mahkota Goryeo.</font>

129
00:11:37,190 --> 00:11:38,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa menemuinya.</font>

130
00:11:56,310 --> 00:11:57,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyungnim.</font>

131
00:12:08,830 --> 00:12:09,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyungnim?</font>

132
00:12:46,129 --> 00:12:48,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sudah tidak waras.</font>

133
00:13:07,350 --> 00:13:08,519
<font color=#FFFF00>Berikan itu.</font>

134
00:13:09,519 --> 00:13:10,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini bukan makanan.</font>

135
00:13:18,999 --> 00:13:20,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia berada di kuil...</font>

136
00:13:21,259 --> 00:13:23,529
<font color=#FFFF00>...saat Ratu mengirimnya kue.</font>

137
00:13:23,999 --> 00:13:25,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada orang-orang...</font>

138
00:13:25,999 --> 00:13:27,739
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang menyebabkannya demam tinggi.</font>

139
00:13:28,100 --> 00:13:29,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Sejak dulu,</font>

140
00:13:29,739 --> 00:13:31,139
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia sudah seperti ini.</font>

141
00:13:34,580 --> 00:13:36,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bicara omong kosong.</font>

142
00:13:36,350 --> 00:13:38,649
<font color=#FFFF00>Tabib yang menerima...</font>

143
00:13:39,680 --> 00:13:41,279
<font color=#FFFF00>...kue yang diracuni itu,</font>

144
00:13:42,149 --> 00:13:44,889
<font color=#FFFF00>...ditemukan tewas keesokan harinya.</font>

145
00:13:49,930 --> 00:13:52,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Tuan Eun akan menemui Ratu.</font>

146
00:13:58,229 --> 00:13:59,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Untuk membicarakan pernikahan.</font>

147
00:14:00,340 --> 00:14:03,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Pernikahan apa?/
Pernikahanmu dan Nona San.</font>

148
00:14:04,210 --> 00:14:06,879
<font color=#FFFF00>Kudengar Ayahmu sudah setuju.</font>

149
00:14:07,139 --> 00:14:08,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau...</font>

150
00:14:09,249 --> 00:14:10,609
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak menyadari itu?</font>

151
00:14:24,460 --> 00:14:26,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Tuan Eun sudah meninggal.</font>

152
00:14:29,430 --> 00:14:34,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yakin ada
hubungannya dengan Ratu.</font>

153
00:14:34,899 --> 00:14:37,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Tuan Eun?/
Ya, Raja.</font>

154
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:39,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia ingin mendapatkan uangnya...</font>

155
00:14:39,940 --> 00:14:42,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya./
Jadi dia membunuhnya?</font>

156
00:14:42,350 --> 00:14:44,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yakin itu.</font>

157
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:47,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu Seja?</font>

158
00:14:47,550 --> 00:14:50,519
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu dan anak sangat dekat.</font>

159
00:14:51,090 --> 00:14:54,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku berasumsi kalau mereka merencanakan
ini bersama-sama.</font>

160
00:14:58,029 --> 00:14:59,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku telah membawa...</font>

161
00:15:00,159 --> 00:15:02,800
<font color=#FFFF00>...ular berbisa di tanahku sendiri.</font>

162
00:15:04,700 --> 00:15:06,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Ular berbisa itu...</font>

163
00:15:06,999 --> 00:15:09,170
<font color=#FFFF00>...melahirkan ular berbisa lagi.</font>

164
00:15:12,239 --> 00:15:14,739
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan membiarkan semua ini.</font>

165
00:15:30,659 --> 00:15:31,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang anda lakukan?</font>

166
00:15:31,790 --> 00:15:34,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia berani memfitnah namaku.</font>

167
00:15:34,229 --> 00:15:36,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bertanya apa itu milik Ayahku./
Diam.</font>

168
00:15:36,729 --> 00:15:38,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan padaku!</font>

169
00:15:38,369 --> 00:15:40,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau menuduhku?</font>

170
00:15:46,739 --> 00:15:47,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir.</font>

171
00:15:49,680 --> 00:15:50,850
<font color=#FFFF00>San.</font>

172
00:15:58,119 --> 00:15:59,259
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan.</font>

173
00:16:05,499 --> 00:16:06,729
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan lakukan ini.</font>

174
00:16:08,560 --> 00:16:10,869
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia baru saja kehilangan Ayahnya.</font>

175
00:16:10,869 --> 00:16:12,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa anda harus...</font>

176
00:16:12,340 --> 00:16:14,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak!/
San.</font>

177
00:16:14,570 --> 00:16:17,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahku baik-baik saja.
Pil ini akan...</font>

178
00:16:17,009 --> 00:16:18,639
<font color=#FFFF00>Ketika aku tiba di sana, dia sudah...</font>

179
00:16:20,379 --> 00:16:22,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah memanggil tabib kerajaan,
tapi aku terlambat.</font>

180
00:16:23,850 --> 00:16:25,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahmu...</font>

181
00:16:27,749 --> 00:16:28,989
<font color=#FFFF00>...sudah meninggal.</font>

182
00:16:36,529 --> 00:16:37,690
<font color=#FFFF00>San.</font>

183
00:17:15,830 --> 00:17:19,070
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ratu menginginkan kekayaan Tuan Eun.</i></font>

184
00:17:19,399 --> 00:17:21,899
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia harus mendapatkan
apa yang dia butuh.</i></font>

185
00:17:22,669 --> 00:17:24,169
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau harus tahu itu.</i></font>

186
00:17:26,010 --> 00:17:28,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Tuan Lin, anda tidak boleh masuk.</font>

187
00:17:28,810 --> 00:17:31,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika anda memaksa,
kami harus menangkapmu.</font>

188
00:17:31,250 --> 00:17:33,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa Menteri
Keuangan datang ke istana?</font>

189
00:17:34,219 --> 00:17:36,449
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia datang tadi pagi./
Apa dia masih di sini?</font>

190
00:17:36,449 --> 00:17:38,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak melihat dia pergi.</font>

191
00:17:39,889 --> 00:17:41,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu Nona San?</font>

192
00:17:41,560 --> 00:17:43,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia juga datang?
Tadi pagi.</font>

193
00:17:43,790 --> 00:17:46,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia masuk ke kamar Ratu.</font>

194
00:17:46,260 --> 00:17:47,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ada sesuatu yang terjadi?</font>

195
00:17:48,230 --> 00:17:51,770
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Mereka sangat cantik saat berlari.
Bahkan saat diam.</i></font>

196
00:17:51,770 --> 00:17:53,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Apalagi saat tidur.</font>

197
00:17:54,439 --> 00:17:55,639
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku./
Untuk apa?</font>

198
00:18:04,750 --> 00:18:06,649
<font color=#FFFF00>Tuan Lin, ikut aku.</font>

199
00:18:16,790 --> 00:18:19,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa kau di sini?/
Dimana Nona San?</font>

200
00:18:19,300 --> 00:18:21,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah lupa statusmu?</font>

201
00:18:21,159 --> 00:18:22,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Dimana Tuan Eun?</font>

202
00:18:24,600 --> 00:18:25,869
<font color=#FFFF00>Dimana dia?</font>

203
00:18:27,199 --> 00:18:28,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sudah meninggal.</font>

204
00:18:30,510 --> 00:18:32,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia kemarin baik-baik saja.</font>

205
00:18:32,939 --> 00:18:35,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai hari ini.../
Dia menderita penyakit kronis.</font>

206
00:18:36,050 --> 00:18:37,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi.../
Dimana?</font>

207
00:18:38,649 --> 00:18:40,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Di Wonseongjeon?/
Iya.</font>

208
00:18:41,219 --> 00:18:44,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana dengan Nona San?
Aku akan menjaganya.</font>

209
00:18:46,959 --> 00:18:50,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Tangkap dia, dan bawa keluar dari
istana tanpa ada yang lihat.</font>

210
00:18:54,859 --> 00:18:57,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggir./
Aku melakukan ini untuk menyelamatkanmu.</font>

211
00:18:58,030 --> 00:18:59,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Beraninya kau melanggar perintah itu?</font>

212
00:19:00,600 --> 00:19:02,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau, orang terdekatku,
melanggar perintahku,</font>

213
00:19:02,939 --> 00:19:05,409
<font color=#FFFF00>Otoritas apa yang akan aku
miliki lagi?</font>

214
00:19:06,780 --> 00:19:08,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi pergilah sekarang juga.</font>

215
00:19:11,550 --> 00:19:14,649
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana dia bisa meninggal?/
Aku sudah bilang dia menderita penyakit kronis.</font>

216
00:19:14,649 --> 00:19:16,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia sendirian?</font>

217
00:19:17,689 --> 00:19:19,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang ingin kau tanyakan?/
Apa ada orang...</font>

218
00:19:20,359 --> 00:19:24,159
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang bersamanya dikirim Ratu?</font>

219
00:19:24,889 --> 00:19:28,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa dengan kalian semua?/
Teh beracun, makanan, atau...</font>

220
00:19:28,459 --> 00:19:30,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang ingin kau katakan?</font>

221
00:19:30,969 --> 00:19:33,199
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau menuduh Ibuku?</font>

222
00:19:35,510 --> 00:19:40,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menjaga Menteri
Keuangan sekaligus Nona San.</font>

223
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:42,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yang akan menjaganya./
Aku tidak bisa mempercayaimu.</font>

224
00:19:45,149 --> 00:19:48,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang tidak kau percaya?/
Aku tidak bisa meninggalkan dia...</font>

225
00:19:50,119 --> 00:19:51,959
<font color=#FFFF00>...di istana ini.</font>

226
00:19:52,520 --> 00:19:54,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Lin./
Aku akan...</font>

227
00:19:55,859 --> 00:19:57,260
<font color=#FFFF00>...menjaganya.</font>

228
00:20:27,520 --> 00:20:29,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahku tidak mau minum obatnya.</font>

229
00:20:32,260 --> 00:20:33,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak bernafas.</font>

230
00:20:38,399 --> 00:20:40,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Tubuhnya sangat dingin.</font>

231
00:20:47,510 --> 00:20:48,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus membawanya pulang.</font>

232
00:20:50,310 --> 00:20:51,649
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan mengantarmu.</font>

233
00:20:52,980 --> 00:20:54,119
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo.</font>

234
00:21:42,570 --> 00:21:44,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin pulang kerumah.</font>

235
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:48,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin pulang bersama Ayahku.</font>

236
00:21:57,010 --> 00:21:58,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Jin Gwan, Jang Eui./
Iya.</font>

237
00:21:58,820 --> 00:21:59,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapkan tandu untuknya.</font>

238
00:21:59,980 --> 00:22:01,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Jeoha./
Ya, Jeoha.</font>

239
00:22:01,990 --> 00:22:03,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yang memanggil Wang Lin...</font>

240
00:22:06,919 --> 00:22:08,659
<font color=#FFFF00>...ke istana.</font>

241
00:22:10,129 --> 00:22:11,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan aku memperintahkannya...</font>

242
00:22:13,899 --> 00:22:16,000
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk membawa Menteri Keuangan
kembali kerumahnya dengan selamat.</font>

243
00:22:27,340 --> 00:22:29,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bersumpah, ini pertama
kali aku bertemu dengannya.</font>

244
00:22:29,879 --> 00:22:32,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai Nona San menemukan itu,</font>

245
00:22:32,050 --> 00:22:34,919
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku tidak tahu
obatnya ada di sana.</font>

246
00:22:42,159 --> 00:22:46,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku membawa Nona San kesini sesuai
perintah anda. Aku tidak tahu apa-apa.</font>

247
00:22:46,500 --> 00:22:48,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kau mau?</font>

248
00:22:49,530 --> 00:22:53,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...tidak tahu apa-apa.</font>

249
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:54,969
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan apa yang kau mau.</font>

250
00:22:55,100 --> 00:22:56,709
<font color=#FFFF00>Ratu, tolong...</font>

251
00:22:56,709 --> 00:22:58,469
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan itu...</font>

252
00:22:59,409 --> 00:23:00,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Ratu.</font>

253
00:23:21,859 --> 00:23:24,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau yakin Menteri
Keuangan sudah meninggal?</font>

254
00:23:24,669 --> 00:23:26,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka hanya membiarkannya.</font>

255
00:23:27,199 --> 00:23:30,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia dibunuh?
Tabib ingin memeriksanya,</font>

256
00:23:30,369 --> 00:23:32,010
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi putrinya menghentikan mereka.</font>

257
00:23:32,209 --> 00:23:34,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Seseorang baru
saja meninggal di istanaku.</font>

258
00:23:34,209 --> 00:23:37,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang harus kita katakan?
Para pejabat kerajaan akan membicarakan ini.</font>

259
00:23:37,550 --> 00:23:39,419
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebelum mereka berbicara hal lain,</font>

260
00:23:40,219 --> 00:23:42,449
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku harus mengambil hartanya.</font>

261
00:23:44,750 --> 00:23:47,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika mereka menginginkan hartanya,</font>

262
00:23:47,689 --> 00:23:49,629
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku yang akan mengambilnya
terlebih dahulu.</font>

263
00:23:53,699 --> 00:23:57,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Hal pertama yang aku inginkan
adalah Seja menjadi sendiri.</font>

264
00:23:58,840 --> 00:24:01,969
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak mudah memisahkan
Ratu dan Seja.</font>

265
00:24:02,939 --> 00:24:04,909
<font color=#FFFF00>Ikatan mereka sangat kuat.</font>

266
00:24:05,939 --> 00:24:07,709
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus mencapai
apapun yang sulit.</font>

267
00:24:08,439 --> 00:24:10,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Bahkan jika kita berhasil,</font>

268
00:24:10,810 --> 00:24:14,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang akan terjadi? Orang-orang akan
tetap memuji semua yang dia lakukan.</font>

269
00:24:15,350 --> 00:24:19,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentara bodoh dan pejabat
kerajaan licik itu...</font>

270
00:24:19,020 --> 00:24:22,830
<font color=#FFFF00>...memuji dia tanpa henti sampai
mulutnya kering.</font>

271
00:24:24,629 --> 00:24:26,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Memujinya berarti mereka
berharap banyak.</font>

272
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:29,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Semakin mereka berharap,
semakin mereka kecewa.</font>

273
00:24:30,629 --> 00:24:34,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Sangat mudah
membuat mereka kembali.</font>

274
00:24:35,770 --> 00:24:39,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika berhasil, apa itu
akan menjadi akhir baginya?</font>

275
00:24:39,510 --> 00:24:43,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang terakhir, sahabat dan cintanya
harus berpaling darinya.</font>

276
00:24:45,209 --> 00:24:47,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah saat kita bisa
melihat dia jatuh.</font>

277
00:24:48,449 --> 00:24:49,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia akan jatuh...</font>

278
00:24:51,189 --> 00:24:52,590
<font color=#FFFF00>...atau bereaksi berlebihan karena marah.</font>

279
00:24:57,929 --> 00:25:00,000
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bagaimana sikap Raja?</i></font>

280
00:25:01,300 --> 00:25:04,330
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia tidak pernah bersikap kasar
sejak aku melayaninya.</i></font>

281
00:25:04,469 --> 00:25:07,240
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Obat Bu Yong sangat misterius.</i></font>

282
00:25:07,340 --> 00:25:09,240
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tunggu, apa dia sekarang Ratu Mu?</i></font>

283
00:25:09,510 --> 00:25:11,369
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ratu Mu, Ratu yang
berbeda dengan Ratu lain.</i></font>

284
00:25:52,850 --> 00:25:54,649
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini sudah lama menggangguku.</font>

285
00:25:59,320 --> 00:26:01,119
<font color=#FFFF00>Pembakar dupa yang
tersisa di ruangan ini...</font>

286
00:26:03,730 --> 00:26:05,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini bukan pembakar dupa yang biasa mereka
gunakan di Wonseongjeon.</font>

287
00:26:07,359 --> 00:26:09,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibuku sangat suka terhadap wewangian.</font>

288
00:26:12,340 --> 00:26:16,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak tahu apa-apa. Aku diperintahkan
untuk membersihkan tempat ini.</font>

289
00:26:16,609 --> 00:26:18,409
<font color=#FFFF00>Menyelip di tengah malam...</font>

290
00:26:19,439 --> 00:26:20,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa?</font>

291
00:26:21,780 --> 00:26:23,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak tahu.</font>

292
00:26:23,449 --> 00:26:25,179
<font color=#FFFF00>Cari tahu itu./
Ya, Jeoha.</font>

293
00:26:25,820 --> 00:26:28,619
<font color=#FFFF00>Tabib kerajaan sudah menunggu./
Aku akan segera menyerahkannya.</font>

294
00:26:33,459 --> 00:26:35,020
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku tidak bisa mempercayaimu.</i></font>

295
00:26:35,959 --> 00:26:37,330
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku tidak bisa meninggalkan dia...</i></font>

296
00:26:38,429 --> 00:26:40,159
<font color=#FFFF00>...di istana ini.</font>

297
00:26:41,060 --> 00:26:42,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Lin./
Aku akan...</font>

298
00:26:44,169 --> 00:26:45,469
<font color=#FFFF00>...menjaganya.</font>

299
00:26:49,139 --> 00:26:50,510
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku ingin pulang kerumah.</i></font>

300
00:26:51,369 --> 00:26:53,709
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin pulang bersama Ayahku.</font>

301
00:27:00,250 --> 00:27:02,419
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha. Jeoha.</font>

302
00:27:03,919 --> 00:27:07,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini dupa perangsang yang dibuat dengan
zat kelenjar rusa jantan dan jingyeongcho.</font>

303
00:27:08,020 --> 00:27:09,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Perangsang?</font>

304
00:27:09,260 --> 00:27:11,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Jingyeongcho tidak
tumbuh didaerah ini...</font>

305
00:27:11,359 --> 00:27:13,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa efeknya jika digunakan pada
orang yang mengalami penyakit jantung?</font>

306
00:27:13,959 --> 00:27:18,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini sangat berbahaya. Ini
bisa merangsang peredaran darahnya...</font>

307
00:27:18,600 --> 00:27:20,800
<font color=#FFFF00>...sehingga menyebabkan kesulitan bernafas
dan juga serangan jantung.</font>

308
00:27:24,340 --> 00:27:26,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Nyonya rumah itu
bekerja di Wonseongjeon.</font>

309
00:27:26,409 --> 00:27:29,449
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia mengaku kalau itu
perintah Ratu...</font>

310
00:27:30,149 --> 00:27:32,179
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk menyelinap membawa keluar
dupa di ruang tamu.</font>

311
00:27:33,179 --> 00:27:34,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa mengkonfirmasinya
pada Ratu.</font>

312
00:30:23,290 --> 00:30:24,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Istirahatlah.</font>

313
00:30:26,619 --> 00:30:27,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Tarik napas dalam-dalam.</font>

314
00:30:31,159 --> 00:30:32,699
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus istirahat.</font>

315
00:30:35,699 --> 00:30:36,869
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak apa.</font>

